Program: Crossing Continents
Title: Southern Sudan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00lvh19
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 10 Aug 2009
While the world's attention has focused on the conflict in Darfur, an older and even bloodier conflict between the Muslim north and mainly Christian south of Sudan is in danger of reigniting. Four years after a peace deal was agreed, Grant Ferrett travels to Southern Sudan to investigate claims that Africa's biggest nation is sliding back to civil war. Show less